cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","label":"Cron: 空闲检测自主学习","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-main-cron-3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1775098760711,"sessionId":"3b277775-5ea4-4212-ab6a-b0e7d5abf051","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":45572,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/3b277775-5ea4-4212-ab6a-b0e7d5abf051.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这是一个定时任务，需要我：\n1. 查询 sessions_list 检查是否有活跃对话（最近5分钟内的用户消息）\n2. 如果没有活跃对话，执行自主学习（搜索行业动态并保存到学习笔记）\n3. 如果有活跃对话，回复\"检测到活跃对话，不执行自主学习\"\n\n让我先查询 sessions_list。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_izljf0jyvnz8_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"activeMinutes":5,"messageLimit":1}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775098761291}]}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775098768936}}
{"type":"message","id":"1e0e6027","parentId":"d14f655e","timestamp":"2026-04-02T02:59:35.742Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"查询结果显示只有1个session，是当前cron任务本身的session（\"agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978\"），这不是与用户的活跃对话。\n\n我需要排除当前cron任务的session，看看是否有其他用户发起的活跃对话。从结果来看，只返回了1个session，就是当前cron的session，没有其他用户活跃对话。\n\n所以应该执行自主学习。让我搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等道简网络相关行业的最新动态。\n\n我需要使用web-search skill来搜索这些信息。让我先读取这个skill文件。","thinkingSignature":"93608e441bde0a261049214482c4288c0b35b827356a276e8b1f8815be424666"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_matp8dbv0u2b_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":932,"output":174,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45087,"cost":{"input":0.00027959999999999997,"output":0.00020879999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0018078299999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775098768941}}
{"type":"message","id":"5893be7d","parentId":"1e0e6027","timestamp":"2026-04-02T02:59:35.752Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_matp8dbv0u2b_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775098775747}}
{"type":"message","id":"49b18521","parentId":"5893be7d","timestamp":"2026-04-02T02:59:41.651Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我知道如何使用web search了。让我搜索几个关键词来获取最新信息：\n1. 企业数字化转型最新动态 2026\n2. 智能安防行业动态 2026\n3. 网络系统集成行业趋势 2026\n4. IT运维服务行业发展\n\n让我执行这些搜索。","thinkingSignature":"2144a9b201234e5e5edc9272925662c4ca76e74312d2abaa0bb5b7bb7158dc0e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ume8n6gv3827_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型最新动态 2026\" 2>/dev/null | head -100"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ume8n6gv3827_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业动态 2026\" 2>/dev/null | head -100"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ume8n6gv3827_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"IT运维服务行业发展趋势 2026\" 2>/dev/null | head -100"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1621,"output":205,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45807,"cost":{"input":0.0004863,"output":0.00024599999999999996,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00205173}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775098775752}}
